===Etymology===
* First attested in mid 15th century.
* From {{etyl|enm|en}} {{m|enm|acrewen}}, from {{etyl|fro|en}} {{m|fro|acreue|acreüe}}, past participle of {{m|fro|accreistre||to increase}}, from {{etyl|la|en}} {{m|la|accrēsco||increase}}, from {{m|la|ad||in addition}} + {{m|la|crēscō||to grow}}.
* Compare [[accretion]], [[accresce]], [[accrete]], [[crew]], [[crescent]].

